{"tid":1757184,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"近排做咩事？休息？","createTime":"2019-11-26T11:35:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-26T13:00:52.000Z","uid":324877,"like":4,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"d065b6a154603edc0e3847615b6a8748d4f52934","tid":1757184,"uid":324877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T11:35:57.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">你哋班休息撚<br />\n休乜撚嘢息呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">好簡單一個道理<br />\n勇武年輕化<br />\n你自己都識講勇武好多1516歲<br />\n你而家復課<br />\n邊撚個同你打呀？<br />\n幾多學校就黎考試<br />\n考試邊撚個同你出呀？</span></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">而家呢個年代興考試唔比出街</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>唔好同我講咩重整旗鼓休息行更長嘅路<br />\n你用你隻眼睇下你個日曆<br />\n11月尾啦 下個月聖誕啦<br />\n想休撚到幾時呀？<br />\n等侵侵簽名？之後又話成功左支線又休息呀？</strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n真係嬲到陣<br />\n唔知做黎為乜<br />\n塞鐵 又係得後生頂 又比人鬧又比人拉<br />\n黎明行動成功得果幾日<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">然之後又話要抖</span></span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n大佬邊度次次都聚到人比你呀<br />\n你哋要幾多個周同學先夠呀？？？？？<br />\n你哋對得住佢哋？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">熊家俊先生（25歲） - 15/12/2017<br />\n梁凌杰先生（35歲） - 15/6/2019<br />\n盧曉欣小姐（21歲） - 30/6/2019<br />\n鄔幸恩小姐（29歲） - 30/6/2019<br />\n麥小姐（28歲） - 3/7/2019<br />\n梅先生（32歲） - 5/7/2019<br />\n范先生（26歲） - 22/7/2019<br />\nCalvin 郭先生（25歲） - 27/8/2019<br />\n姬先生（16歲） - 2/9/2019<br />\n陳彥霖小姐 （15歲） - 19/9/2019<br />\n曾穎欣小姐 （26歲） - 7/11/2019<br />\n周梓樂先生（22歲）- 8/11/2019<br />\n<br />\n元朗恐襲 - 21/7/2019 <br />\n太子慘案 - 31/8/2019 <br />\n荃灣實彈 - 1/10/2019<br />\n西灣河實彈 - 11/11/2019<br />\n圍攻中文大學 - 12/11/2019<br />\n油麻地人踩人 - 18/11/2019 <br />\n圍攻理工大學 - 16/11/2019 至今<br />\n</span></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我求下你哋唔好停啦<br />\n好老實講後生唔撚出邊撚個同你擋子彈呀？</span></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">搞乜鬼野和理非邊個得閒去完你個和理非會又咁得閒再出嚟架？大佬呀而家正常返緊工返緊學架</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">我求下你哋啦唔係一兩日禮拜就贏左呀<br />\n你起碼搞到佢成個教育系統運作唔到先肯停呀<br />\n學生得閒無野做就自然人多啦<br />\n成個停咗後生咪大搖大擺咁行出嚟囉</span></span></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">可能係夢</span></span><br />\n<br />\n唉預撚左比人屌<br />\n你哋要屌便屌要負便負<br />\n真係好撚灰先一個訴求就係咁要休息<br />\n<br />\nSorry可能我衝出嚟柒"},{"pid":"dc39aa939abe92d2799c65213d6b178c48a9984b","tid":1757184,"uid":264783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T11:37:21.000Z","msg":"Support!!"},{"pid":"bfa9ca486359381ad9b88daea87135d8a24ea2f7","tid":1757184,"uid":1477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T11:37:33.000Z","msg":"怕香港人善忘嘅，推行動post 啦<br />\n想聲援理大手足嘅，推行動post 啦<br />\n和理非嘅，推行動post 啦<br />\n勇武嘅，推行動 post 啦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢個係行動post，星期三晚，我地聚首商場，以和理非聲援理大手足<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1756593\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1756593</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"f39c2f89fbe82b8f75b36481e8d9b3255fe2fc1d","tid":1757184,"uid":36471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T11:38:04.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"dcd0b01a21235c06f44b3a94b46dfe12b3deb89c","tid":1757184,"uid":282435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T11:39:06.000Z","msg":"高高高<br />\n<br />\n永續抗爭"},{"pid":"dd261d18705526cb56ae4ee42e561754e3e0622a","tid":1757184,"uid":85725,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T11:39:37.000Z","msg":"你打囉咁叻 喺理大打完嘅傷嘅傷拉嘅拉你估咁易呀